'''Ariane Astrid Atodji''' ;(yavutse 1980), ni Umukinnyi wa firime [[Kameruni]] ndetse akaba n'umwanditsi<ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2011/04/ariane-astrid-atodji-koundi-and.html</ref>.  Yakoze documentaire nyinshi zamamaye cyane harimo ''Koundi et le Jeudi national'' na ''La souffrance est une école de sagesse''<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_liste_generique/C_64777_F</ref> . 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1980 i Nguelemendouka, muri [[Kameruni]].<ref>https://www.3continents.com/en/individu/1924/</ref>  Yarangije muri kaminuza ya Yaoundé hanyuma yitabira amahugurwa ya firime mu kigo cya Goethe muri Yaoundé.<ref>https://www.africapt-festival.fr/real_tous/arianeastrid_atodji.htm</ref> Hanyuma yimukiye muri LN International Film School ya Yaoundé kugirango akomeze kwiga<ref>https://www.crew-united.com/en/Ariane-Astrid-Atodji_277297.html</ref>.<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne-514167/palmares/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu mwaka wa 2010, yayoboye ''filime ye ya mbere ya Koundi et le Jeudi national'' yakozwe ku nkunga ya Goethe Institute<ref>https://www.telerama.fr/cinema/films/la-souffrance-est-une-ecole-de-sagesse,504979.php</ref>.   Yatsindiye igihembo cy’abacamanza kidasanzwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Dubai (DIFF) kubera iyi filime.  Muri 2014, yayoboye documentaire ya kabiri ''La souffrance est une école de sagesse'' <ref>https://nexdimempire.com/tag/ariane-astrid-atodji/</ref>.<ref>https://www.laboutiqueafricavivre.com/films/20709-la-souffrance-est-une-ecole-de-sagesse-3760114952240.html</ref> 

